55:34.340 --> 55:42.080
the institutional boundary should encode rules that prioritize diverse, democratic, human-centric configurations.

55:42.080 --> 55:49.200
The institutions must be fundamentally reprogrammed to protect possibility rather than enforce discipline.

55:49.600 --> 55:52.640
We change the signal from comply to explore.

55:52.800 --> 55:54.880
Precisely. You alter the transmission.

55:55.480 --> 55:58.100
You know, when I try to synthesize all of this,

55:58.200 --> 56:02.400
