56:13.540 --> 56:16.560
But in this framework, emancipation isn't magic.

56:17.060 --> 56:21.780
It is literally just expanding the phase space of what is mathematically possible.

56:22.180 --> 56:26.460
It's giving people room to breathe and make choices beyond mere survival.

56:26.800 --> 56:29.860
It is just changing the geometry of our social reality.

56:29.860 --> 56:34.480
That is the core takeaway of Flyxion's synthesis of Matei.

