56:57.420 --> 57:02.520
You cannot hack a system if you don't know the architecture of its code.

57:02.820 --> 57:03.740
Yeah, to map it first.

57:03.940 --> 57:07.600
And that brings us to the end of an absolutely incredible journey today.

